702059f-a.title: Bronx: Webster Avenue - Gunhill Road (East)
702059f-a.text:
Webster Ave., north from but not including East Gunhill Road, to
East 211th Street (Woodlawn Cemetery), showing the thoroughfare being
repaved by the W.P.A.
December 14, 1936.
Works Progress Administration.

700886f-a.title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Webster Avenue
700886f-a.text:
East Gunhill Road (running from center fore to left background), north
side, west from Webster to Decatur Aves., as seen from underneath the
Third Ave. elevated structure on Webster Ave. The 2-story frame house
bears No. 409, while the 6-story apartment house on the left faces on
Decatur Ave., adjoining the N.E. corner of East Gunhill Road.
May 25, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
